title: The Science of Family Guy with Seth MacFarlane
description: Neil Tyson and his friend Seth MacFarlane delve into the science of “Family Guy”, from the Big Bang to the multiverse. Chuck Nice and Charles Liu join Neil in studio, Simon Singh calls in about math in “The Simpsons”, and Bill Nye gets super-heroic.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
